'''''A Question of Sport''''' is a 1988 [[video game]] based on the [[BBC]] quiz show of the [[Question of Sport|same name]]. As in the show, the player has to answer questions about [[sports]]. The game uses the same [[game engine|engine]] as ''Mike Read's Computer Pop Quiz''.

